    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "The Rooster",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. \r      Today, your four assassination targets have been spreading online misinformation to smear our client. Each of them claimed to be better than our client in singing, dancing, rap, and basketball respectively. Our client, as a real man, cannot tolerate such behavior. We&apos;ve secured a hacker disguise for you. Time is tight on this mission, so I&apos;ll leave you to prepare.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Quartz Tan.\r\rFC72",
